{"tid":889834,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"求推薦高遮瑕BB cushion","createTime":"2018-11-05T00:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T18:25:05.000Z","uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6cc119820d1f7ede03d1864a9cf5b40e3eeece","tid":889834,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T00:26:51.000Z","msg":"我平時化妝唔會上遮瑕，太懶，皮膚主要係黑眼圈勁同額頭多印（面頰有小小）<br />\n<br />\n依加用緊Bobbi Brown<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6tb0x2E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6tb0x2E.png&h=695dfdec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾好用但遮瑕好似又無乜咁<br />\n<br />\n因為係最後一個cushion，所以準備買新嘅<br />\n以前用過April Skin，我記得遮瑕係真係勁，但好似之後嫌個妝感睇落好厚所以轉咗（因為好白，但用22色定23色又太深）<br />\n依排又問過人，佢地又話April Skin會生痘（以前用嗰陣無乜留意）<br />\n<br />\n睇下各位有無乜推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLqkx34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLqkx34.png&h=08f34553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw有無人有用開依隻，琴日都係Youtube睇過啲人實測試用，好似幾好咁，但唔知會唔會好似April Skin咁用得耐會致痘同太死白？因為始終影出嚟同肉眼睇會唔同"},{"pid":"48ecc49a5b7291082f0c2e683f977178413f0658","tid":889834,"uid":172024,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:04:56.000Z","msg":"Mac好似都唔錯～<br />\n懶既我通常係只make up base 再加concealer就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5986b881795e15a074ccc8fbe7bb6a2cbaadf8fc","tid":889834,"uid":177719,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:08:51.000Z","msg":"用開laneige anti aging bb cushion<br />\n我都好多瘡印 但係用左呢個成年都唔駛遮睱<br />\n中意佢夠薄 搽上面貼服<br />\n唔畫眼線淨係上佢同唇膏可以做到偽素顏"},{"pid":"12510edae88251578cb28574c5f3ce5950562763","tid":889834,"uid":209557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:12:45.000Z","msg":"Age's20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 回購咗好多次，好貼同埋保濕而遮瑕方面都幾高，我自己平時